                " Prompt discrete gamma-rays feeding from a neutron",
                " capture state of Ni-62 to low-lying excited states",
                " were observed."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Correction for multiple neutron scattering in carbon",
                " case, nickel and gold samples, and for self-shielding",
